parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt retractor can cause the seatbelt to malfunction, leading to a potential safety risk in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seatbelt fails to retract
the seatbelt becomes unspooled
the seatbelt webbing fails to retract when engaged
the seatbelt is stuck in an extended position
the seatbelt does not latch or retract properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to provide a timely and effective response to the recall can lead to a prolonged period of driving an unsafe vehicle, potentially resulting in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The manufacturer fails to provide a replacement part
the dealer is unable to repair the vehicle due to lack of parts
the manufacturer does not notify the owner of the recall
the owner is not reimbursed for repairs made prior to the recall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front coil spring can cause the tire to blow out, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Loud noises
vibration
and a burning rubber smell from the front end of the vehicle
often accompanied by a sudden drop in the vehicle's height.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to deploy improperly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag malfunction light
inability to repair or replace airbag due to parts unavailability
uncertainty about airbag safety.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Improper airbag deployment can cause serious injury or death, and may not provide adequate protection in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag deployment without crash or impact
airbag failure to deploy in a crash
uneven airbag deployment (e.g.
passenger airbag deploying without passenger present).

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt and Airbag System Malfunctions
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctions in the seat belt and airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Seat belt retractor malfunction
airbag inflator defect
inability to disconnect airbag
uncertainty about airbag safety.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate repair and response to airbag and seat belt system malfunctions can lead to continued risk of injury or death.
symptoms: Unavailability of repair parts
lack of communication from manufacturer or dealer
inability to repair or replace airbag due to liability concerns.
